      "y": 1900,
      "width": 670,
      "height": 70,
      "text": "Emission Factor Sources:\n• ADEME Base Carbone v23 (2024) — French standard factors\n• IEA 2024 World Energy Outlook — global grid factors\n• STEG Sustainability Report 2023 — Tunisian grid: 0.480 kgCO₂/kWh (Scope 2)\n• IPCC AR6 Annex II (2021) — GWP values, Scope 1 combustion factors\n• Natural Gas: 0.205 kgCO₂/kWh (NCV basis) • Diesel: 0.271 kgCO₂/kWh • LPG: 0.227 kgCO₂/kWh",
